<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Notebook Entry</div>
<dl id="n03003d"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n03" href="#n03003d">N03 (VI.B.3)</a>:  <a href="../../FF/fnbs/n03all.htm#n03003d"> 3(d)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> Valery (pupil)</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources"> <font color="green">[Columbanus]</font> loved tenderly St. <mark>Valery</mark>, a shepherd boy, who became one of his monks, and who had charge of the novices&apos; garden, and always held it as a mark of divine favour, that no flowers smelt so sweet, and no vegetables were so fresh as those of his dear brother Valery. <small> J.M. Flood, <a name="JMFI" href="../../FF/fdra/fdex.htm#JMFI"><cite title="source">Ireland: Its Saints and Scholars</cite></a> (n.d) 36</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
